message.body: Hello there! Are you coming out to play tonight?
No. I've been out since 8 and now I'm eating with the fam at fat salmon. In exhausted and spent way too much money already. Hahaha.
Hahahah damn, sounds like someone really took advantage of Black Friday huh? ;) I've never been to Fat Salmon, heard it was good. Okay, now I want sushi!
